headline: Cloudflare Acquires Eager to Reimagine Apps
keywords: Life @ Cloudflare, Cloudflare Apps, Acquisitions, Developers, Programming
description: In 2011 we launched the Cloudflare Apps platform in an article that described Cloudflare as “not ... the sexiest business in the world.” Sexy or not, Cloudflare has since grown from the 3.5 billion pageviews a month we were doing then to over 1.3 trillion per month today.
